T11TD4214E:255a-1: sam bandha pa r'ikshi pra ka ra na /
T11TD4214E:255a-3: 'brel pa brtag pa'i rab tu byed pa /
T11TD4214E:255a-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T11TD4214E:255a-5: gzhan dbang kho nar 'brel pa ni //
T11TD4214E:255a-6: grub pa na gzhan dbang ci zhig yod //
T11TD4214E:255a-7: de phyir dngos po thams cad kyi //
T11TD4214E:255a-8: 'brel pa yang dag nyid du med //
T11TD4214E:255a-10: gnyis nyid yin na ji ltar 'gyur //
T11TD4214E:255a-11: de phyir rang bzhin tha dad pa //
T11TD4214E:255a-12: 'brel pa yang dag nyid du med //
T11TD4214E:255a-13: gzhan ltos pa ni 'brel par yang //
T11TD4214E:255a-14: med na de ni ji ltar ltos //
T11TD4214E:255a-15: yod na'ang kun la rag ma las //
T11TD4214E:255a-16: dngos po ji ltar ltos pa yin //
T11TD4214E:255a-17: gnyis ni 'brel pa gcig pu yis //
T11TD4214E:255a-18: ci ste 'brel na de dang gnyis //
T11TD4214E:255a-19: 'brel pa gang yin thug pa med //
T11TD4214E:255a-20: de bzhin 'brel med shes par bya //
T11TD4214E:255a-21: dngos po de gnyis de las gzhan //
T11TD4214E:255a-22: de dag thams cad bdag nyid gnas //
T11TD4214E:255a-23: de bas rang dngos ma 'dres la //
T11TD4214E:255a-24: de dag rtogs pas 'dres par byed //
T11TD4214E:255a-25: dngos po tha dad rtogs bya'i phyir //
T11TD4214E:255a-26: de yi rjes su 'brang ba yis //
T11TD4214E:255a-27: bya dang byed pa po yi tshig / smra ba po dag 'god par byed //
T11TD4214E:255a-29: de gnyis lhan cig mi gnas pas //
T11TD4214E:255a-30: gnyis la gnas pa ji ltar grub //
T11TD4214E:255a-31: gnyis la mi gnas ji ltar 'brel //
T11TD4214E:255a-32: rim las dngos po gcig la gnas //
T11TD4214E:255a-33: gzhan la re ba med pa yin //
T11TD4214E:255a-34: de med par yang yod pa'i phyir //
T11TD4214E:255a-35: gcig la gnas pa 'brel pa med //
T11TD4214E:255a-37: ci ste de ni gcig la ltos //
T11TD4214E:255a-38: ltos pa phan pa byed par 'gyur //
T11TD4214E:255a-39: med na ji ltar phan par byed //
T11TD4214E:255a-40: ci ste don gcig 'brel pa'i phyir //
T11TD4214E:255a-41: de gnyis rgyu 'bras nyid yin na //
T11TD4214E:255a-42: gnyis nyid la sogs 'brel pa'i phyir //
T11TD4214E:255a-43: g-yas g-yon rva yang de nyid 'thob //
T11TD4214E:255a-45: de mtshan de las gzhan du min //
T11TD4214E:255a-46: yod dang med pa'i bye brag can //
T11TD4214E:255b-0: sbyor ba ci ste rgyu 'bras @255b na //
T11TD4214E:255b-1: sbyor ba'i bye brag can de nyid //
T11TD4214E:255b-3: tha dad ces bya'i sgra 'di ni //
T11TD4214E:255b-4: smra byed la brten ma yin nam //
T11TD4214E:255b-5: gang zhig mthong na ma mthong mthong //
T11TD4214E:255b-6: de ma mthong na ma mthong ba //
T11TD4214E:255b-7: 'bras bu yin pa nyid du ni //
T11TD4214E:255b-8: ston pa'i skye bo med par shes //
T11TD4214E:255b-9: mthong dang ma mthong ma gtogs par //
T11TD4214E:255b-10: 'bras bu'i blo ni mi srid phyir //
T11TD4214E:255b-12: tha snyad sla ba'i phyir bkod do //
T11TD4214E:255b-13: de yod yod phyir de 'bras rtogs //
T11TD4214E:255b-14: gang yang rjes su smra ba yi //
T11TD4214E:255b-15: brda yi yul du de brjod de //
T11TD4214E:255b-16: lkog shal la sogs glang rtogs bzhin //
T11TD4214E:255b-17: yod 'gyur yod na de yod cing //
T11TD4214E:255b-18: yod pa nyid na'ang yod 'gyur ba //
T11TD4214E:255b-19: ngon sum mi dmigs pa dag las //
T11TD4214E:255b-20: rgyu 'bras kho nar rab tu grub //
T11TD4214E:255b-21: re zhig de tsam yang dag don //
T11TD4214E:255b-22: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i spyod yul rnams //
T11TD4214E:255b-23: rnam par rtog pas ston pa ni //
T11TD4214E:255b-24: don log pa yi don bzhin ston //
T11TD4214E:255b-25: tha dad yin na ci zhig 'brel //
T11TD4214E:255b-26: tha dad min na rgyu 'bras gang //
T11TD4214E:255b-27: gzhan zhig yod na ma 'brel gnyis //
T11TD4214E:255b-28: de gnyis 'brel pa ji ltar byed //
T11TD4214E:255b-29: sbyor dang 'du ba la sogs pa //
T11TD4214E:255b-30: thams cad des kyang dpyad pa yin //
T11TD4214E:255b-31: phan tshun phan pa mi byed phyir //
T11TD4214E:255b-34: 'bras bu skyed par byed na yang //
T11TD4214E:255b-36: shin tu thal phyir de gnyis min //
T11TD4214E:255b-37: de gnyis dang ni 'du ba dang //
T11TD4214E:255b-38: gzhan yang phan pa mi byed par //
T11TD4214E:255b-39: ci ste 'brel na mtha' dag kyang //
T11TD4214E:255b-41: la sogs sbyor ba can grub phyir //
T11TD4214E:255b-42: sbyor ba skyed kyang des de gnyis //
T11TD4214E:255b-43: sbyor ba can du mi 'dod de //
T11TD4214E:255b-44: gnas par byed pa'ang rab tu brjod //
T11TD4214E:255b-45: sbyor ba la sogs pa yi gnas //
T11TD4214E:255b-46: rung ba'i dngos po de 'gyur na //
T11TD4214E:255b-47: rung ba'i dngos po rtag na ni //
T11TD4214E:255b-48: de dang bral bar 'gal phyir ro //
T11TD4214E:255b-49: de bas bral dang ldan pa dang //
T11TD4214E:255b-50: 'gro sogs rung ba brjod pa na //
T11TD4214E:255b-51: ngo bo 'di la nges par brjod //
T11TD4214E:255b-52: 'gro sogs gzhan rtags ci zhig bya //
T11TD4214E:255b-53: de dag rnams la yod na yang //
T11TD4214E:255b-55: skad cig so sor skye ba yi //
T11TD4214E:255b-56: dngos po tha dad 'di yin rigs /
T11TD4214E:256a-0: @256a * // 'brel pa brtag pa'i rab tu byed pa /
T11TD4214E:256a-1: slob dpon mkhas pa chen po chos kyi grags pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T11TD4214E:256a-3: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzny'a na garbha dang /
T11TD4214E:256a-4: lo ts'a ba bande nam mkhas bsgyur /
T11TD4214E:256a-5: slad kyi pandi ta rab 'byor zhi ba dang /
T11TD4214E:256a-6: lo ts'a ba ting nge 'dzin bzang pos bcos shing gtan la phab pa//
